                                        p.pagraph Yes, the Base Interest Rate applies if your MaxiGain account has a minimum balance of S$10,000. In other words, base interest accrues on a day where the account balance for that day is at least S$10,000. Conversely, no base interest shall accrue on a day where the account balance for that day falls below S$10,000.
